'''Balosur''' or '''Balosar''' was the native tongue of the [[Balosar (species)/Legends|Balosar]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Balosar/Legends|Balosar]]. It was a [[Written Balosar|crudely-written]] language made of throaty rasps and deep vocalizations. Written Balosur seemed less complex than written [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] due to its crude aspect, but in fact was considered to be no less complex than Basic. Notably, the non-Balosar [[Marcus Sione]] had learned the language and spoke it fluently.<ref name="CATCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

